<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Travel is better together.</h2>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">✈️</div>
      <h3>Share your flights</h3>
      <p>Post your upcoming trips and see which friends are flying the same routes. Coordinate effortlessly without the group chat chaos.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">💸</div>
      <h3>Split costs instantly</h3>
      <p>Split baggage fees, lounge passes, and travel expenses with your crew. Everyone pays their share — no awkward IOUs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
      <h3>Smart flight alerts</h3>
      <p>Get notified when a friend books a route you're watching. Never miss a chance to fly together again.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

<!-- PRIVACY POLICY -->
<section class="privacy-section" id="privacy">
  <div class="section-label">Legal</div>
  <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Privacy Policy</h2>
  <div class="prose">
    <p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>Flair collects only the information necessary to provide our flight-sharing service. This includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Account information (name, email address)</li>
      <li>Flight details you choose to share within the app</li>
      <li>Device information for app functionality and crash reporting</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use your data</h2>
    <p>Your data is used solely to power the Flair experience — matching you with friends on the same routes, enabling cost splitting, and sending relevant flight notifications. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p>

    <h2>Data sharing</h2>
    <p>Flight information you post is visible to your connected friends within Flair. You control who can see your trips at all times. We do not share your data with advertisers or data brokers.</p>

    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your account data for as long as your account is active. You may delete your account at any time, which will remove all associated personal data within 30 days.</p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@flairapp.com">privacy@flairapp.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Reach out at <a href="mailto:privacy@flairapp.com">privacy@flairapp.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

<!-- SUPPORT -->
<section class="support-section" id="support">
  <div class="section-label">Support</div>
  <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 0;">Need help?</h2>
